# Spoke scaffold ignore — v4-era (mode-agnostic: matches v3 WAI-Spoke/ and v4 WAI-Harness/spoke/local/)
# Track durable work-state; ignore only regenerable runtime, caches, secrets.

# regenerable runtime (any tree depth)
**/runtime/
**/.autosave/
**/*-brief.json

# build / OS
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.DS_Store
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
*.swp
*.swo

# secrets / local-only (never commit)
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/.provider

# === Secrets & artifacts baseline (Fable MR-1) — never commit ===
# Root cause of the fleet's #1 risk: an absent/one-line .gitignore. This block is the
# reusable baseline. Keep templates tracked via the negations; everything else is ignored.
# env files (all variants) — but keep the committed templates
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.template
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.sample
# private keys / certs / keystores
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.keystore
*.jks
id_rsa
id_dsa
id_ecdsa
id_ed25519
# cloud / service credentials & tokens
**/credentials.json
**/client_secret*.json
**/service-account*.json
**/*-service-account*.json
**/gha-creds-*.json
token.json
*.token
*token*.pickle
*.pickle
*.pkl
.aws/
.gcloud/
gcloud-*.json
# browser credential stores / OS cruft / Windows
**/Login Data
**/Cookies
*:Zone.Identifier
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
# build artifacts / dependencies (regenerable)
node_modules/
.next/
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo
# runtime data dumps (the nurturator/pathfinder leak class) — un-ignore tracked sets with !data/<path>
**/data/runtime/
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
# === END Secrets & artifacts baseline ===

# === WAI managed: regenerable advisor/runtime state (idempotent block) ===
WAI-Harness/spoke/local/runtime/
WAI-Harness/spoke/local/wakeup-brief.json
WAI-Harness/spoke/advisors/*/scan_state.json
WAI-Harness/spoke/advisors/*/passes.jsonl
WAI-Harness/spoke/advisors/*/vectors.jsonl
WAI-Harness/spoke/advisors/*/findings-log.jsonl
WAI-Harness/hub/local/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/scan_state.json
WAI-Harness/hub/local/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/passes.jsonl
WAI-Harness/hub/local/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/vectors.jsonl
WAI-Harness/hub/local/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/findings-log.jsonl
WAI-Harness/hub/local/autopilot/wheel-activity.html
WAI-Harness/hub/local/autopilot/runs.jsonl
# v3 fallback
WAI-Spoke/runtime/
WAI-Spoke/advisors/*/scan_state.json
# === END WAI managed ===
